===參與國家及地區===
共有32個國家參賽（包括2個受邀國家）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://sapporo2017.org/site/news-en/12161.html |title=2017 Sapporo AWG sport entries by NOC |date=2016-12-16 |website=www.sapporo2017.org |publisher=8th Sapporo Asian Winter Games Organizing Committee |access-date=2016-12-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220185609/https://sapporo2017.org/site/news-en/12161.html |archivedate=2016-12-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1045043/thirty-one-countries-confirmed-for-asian-winter-games-in-sapporo |title=Thirty-one countries confirmed for Asian Winter Games in Sapporo |last=Palmer |first=Dan |date=2016-12-20 |website=Insidethegames.biz |publisher=Dunsar Media |access-date=2016-12-20 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222220033/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1045043/thirty-one-countries-confirmed-for-asian-winter-games-in-sapporo |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

印尼、斯里蘭卡、東帝汶、土庫曼和越南將首次參賽<ref name="a">{{cite web |url=http://www.ocasia.org/News/IndexNewsRM.aspx?WKegervtea351JtiByG9Lw== |title=OCA prepares for winter sports celebration at Sapporo 2017 |date=2016-04-27 |website=Olympic Council of Asia |publisher=[[Olympic_Council_of_Asia|Olympic Council of Asia]] |access-date=2016-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807030548/http://www.ocasia.org/News/IndexNewsRM.aspx?WKegervtea351JtiByG9Lw== |archive-date=2016-08-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。另有3個國家計畫參賽：阿富汗（沒有在截止日期前提出申請）、柬埔寨和伊拉克（因為非[[國際滑冰聯盟|國際滑冰聯盟]]會員國，參賽申請被拒絕）。而[[巴林|巴林]]則於比賽前宣佈退賽。

由於科威特政府干預國內奧林匹克運動，國際奧委會對科威特奧委會全球禁賽，科威特運動員以個人名義參加本屆冬季賽事，升五環旗、奏奧林匹克會歌奧林匹克頌。科威特运动员还以个人名义参加2010年广州亚运会、2011年亚洲冬季运动会。

2016年9月宣布邀請大洋洲運動員參賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1043168/athletes-from-oceania-granted-permission-to-compete-at-sapporo-2017-by-organising-committee |title=Athletes from Oceania granted permission to compete at Sapporo 2017 by Organising Committee |last=Morgan |first=Liam |date=2016-10-30 |website=Insidethegames.biz |publisher=Dunsar Media |access-date=2017-01-02 |archive-date=2017-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102172402/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1043168/athletes-from-oceania-granted-permission-to-compete-at-sapporo-2017-by-organising-committee |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="oceania">{{cite web |url=http://aroundtherings.com/site/A__58044/Title__Australia-to-send-34-athletes-to-OCA/292/Articles |title=Australia to send 34 athletes to OCA's 8th Asian Winter Games Sapporo 2017 |date=2016-11-14 |website=www.aroundtherings.com/ |publisher=[[Around_the_Rings|Around the Rings]] |access-date=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2016-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161115193257/http://aroundtherings.com/site/A__58044/Title__Australia-to-send-34-athletes-to-OCA/292/Articles |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。大洋洲國家的運動員是單獨列出，不是為官方參賽者，是特邀嘉賓（因此不會頒發獎牌，但成績可決定[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会|次年平昌冬奧]]的參賽資格）<ref name="oceania"/>。

